thread.title: Demi

author: Demi
title: Demi
text:
I recently purchased a brand new Corolla from Motorama Toyota in Moorooka and received excellent service.
Kelly Power went above and beyond to get me the car I wanted even though it meant sending it in interstate.
Jonathan Clay helped us with the financial side and explained things to me in a way that I could easily understand.
From our first meeting right up until pick up day, the customer service was an easy 10 out of 10 and I highly recommend everyone buy there next Toyota from Motorama Moorooka.
